mixin block-submit( submit )
    .block-submit
        form.form( method='post' action='action.php' )
            .form__row.form__row--primary
                input.form__email( type='email' name='email' placeholder='Адрес эл. почты' )
                input.form__submit( type='submit' name='submit' placeholder=submit )= submit
            .form__row
                input.form__check( type='checkbox' id='form-check' checked )
                label.form__label(for='form-check') Я согласен с <a href='#0'>условиями оказания услуги</a>
